<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.7">
<l>yāṉoṭṭi yeṉṉu ḷiruttuva ṉeṉṟilaṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉoṭṭi vanteṉ ṟaṉineñcai vañcit</l>
<l>tūṉoṭṭi niṉṟe ṉuyiril kalan tiyal</l>
<l>vāṉoṭṭu mōviṉi yeṉṉai nekiḻkkavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not say “I will stick [and] let [him] be in my heart.</l>
<l>He, sticking, coming, deceiving my solitary heart</l>
<l>sticking to [my] flesh, constantly mingled with my life breath,</l>
<l>will his kind stick when they cut me loose?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
